# VidyaConnect- Enhanced Entity-Relationship (EER) Diagram

## Overview

This repository contains the Enhanced Entity-Relationship (EER) Diagram for the **VidyaConnect** project. The diagram illustrates the logical database design, including entities, attributes, primary keys, foreign keys, relationships, and cardinality constraints.

